summary: L'entusiasmo per un film o per un libro
title: L'entusiasmo per un film o per un libro
body:
L’entusiasmo per un film o per un libro

Ieri su Facebook scrivevo che non sono psicologicamente pronto per vedere Avengers Endgame.
Esagerazione? Iperbole?
Non del tutto.
Per indole sono un entusiasta, ma non un emotivo. Vale a dire che mi entusiasmo per qualche film o libro che ritengo molto nelle mie corde, ma che non mi capita praticamente mai di commuovermi. Fanno eccezione i film in cui muoiono dei cani (maledetti sceneggiatori!).
Gli…

summary:
A sweet little update  No Strings On Me - Chapter 8: Dance (on Wattpad) https://my.w.tt/nPj5RaI4YV

His orders were simple....
caption:
A sweet little update 

No Strings On Me - Chapter 8: Dance (on Wattpad) https://my.w.tt/nPj5RaI4YV His orders were simple. Bring in the little girl with the big brown eyes. But looking into those eyes Bucky couldn’t do it. Instead he decided to take the little girl named Renee and go on the run with her. No more Strings would hold any of them back. They were both free to have a life. But life isn’t always normal. Sometimes life is just crazy.

summary: From all the Avengers Endgame trailers and TV spots I've seen (I haven't seen the leaked video), the movie's starting to look...
body:
From all the Avengers Endgame trailers and TV spots I’ve seen (I haven’t seen the leaked video), the movie’s starting to look like it’s gonna be like Star Trek: The Next Generation’s All Good Things End, to me at least.

If it’s like All Good Things End, it’s gonna be awesome.

title: A minute of meaningless thoughts
body:
When I watched the trailers for Endgame, I had the impression that many actions take place in the headquarters. 

It looks like heroes have a party throughout the film and Thanos comes to them cuz he wasn’t invited.  

No, I didn’t get high
